<span style="font-family:'Century Gothic', sans-serif;font-size:14px;"><p><h2>How to update your font in an email template</h2></p>
<p>After you have saved your signature, scroll down to ‘Message format’.</p>
<p>In the font options, select ‘Century Gothic’ from the drop-down box</p>
<p>In the font size, choose your preference between 10-12 </p>
<p>Select Save at the bottom of page.</p>
